data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Beautiful well-maintained home with 3 sides masonry is located in the highly desired Alamo Ranch. This 3-bedroom 2- bath is a MUST SEE! Brand new carpets in 2 bedrooms. Home has a very open floor plan. The home has ceramic tile throughout the kitchen area and hard flooring throughout majority of the home. Enjoy morning coffee or evenings under your covered patio. Sellers are motivated and will consider all reasonable offers! *Refrigerator stays and home is equiped with water softener staying as well! PLEASE VERIFY ALL SCHOOL, TAX, HOA AND ROOM SIZES.
